d to pay\u00A0for the Libreria as well as for the tombs. Finding\u00A0that he has no such orders, I have as you advised\u00A0refrained from beginning the said work, for it cannot be done without money. When it is settled that the work is to be done, I beg of you to get it arranged in Rome that the payments here are made by Lo Spina, for it would be impossible to find a more suitable man, or one who would carry out his duties with more zeal and attention.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"93468a5c-81bb-40e1-9e2c-9bb1e02e2969","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":22,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"702145da-614b-427d-be35-7a912a76e59d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":22,"value":"a4393234-2745-42ec-ba3e-42e4c52edb0c","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":["0|0|name|Giovanni Francesco Fattucci","1|name|Giovanni Francesco Fattucci"]},{"id":"4cc51989-f141-4da9-b250-58deec845c56","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":32,"end":32,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":["0|0|0|name|Michelangelo Buonarroti (b. 1475/03/06 - d. 1564/02/18)","1|1|name|Michelangelo Buonarroti (b. 1475/03/06 - d. 1564/02/18)","2|name|Michelangelo Buonarroti (b. 1475/03/06 - d. 1564/02/18)"]},{"id":"57ecfb45-ce76-4d1f-a97e-baa90c3e53f8","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":43,"end":46,"value":"a4393234-2745-42ec-ba3e-42e4c52edb0c","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":["0|name|Giovanni Francesco Fattucci"]},{"id":"ac3915d5-6ffb-461e-a5e8-0707005d8b11","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":60,"end":60,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":["0|0|name|Michelangelo Buonarroti (b. 1475/03/06 - d. 1564/02/18)","1|name|Michelangelo Buonarroti (b. 1475/03/06 - d. 1564/02/18)"]},{"id":"3457daf2-70d2-4aed-b124-cbf5df97e493","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":78,"end":85,"value":"294657ae-1ba6-4fd0-8196-b335b7ac54f3","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":["0|0|0|name|Lo Spina","1|1|name|Lo Spina","2|name|Lo Spina"]