9f0-fa33-41d1-a4f6-0545bb7d1b1e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":408,"end":411,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":["0|0|name|Rome","1|name|Rome"]},{"id":"2fac2524-74c3-40b7-90f6-045162060821","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":431,"end":434,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d3ebc0cc-6f09-4329-afc6-345e96c52686","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":448,"end":455,"value":"294657ae-1ba6-4fd0-8196-b335b7ac54f3","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":["0|0|name|Lo Spina","1|name|Lo Spina"]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"2451fca9-9471-4f81-8c60-e055001c6562","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"773fe3dc-1949-4a9c-9faa-9250cc0fda32","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"As for beginning the work, I must wait until the\u00A0marble arrives; I do not believe it will ever arrive, so\u00A0great is the confusion! I could write to you of things\u00A0that would astonish you, only I should never be believed. But enough\u00A0\u2014\u00A0it has been my ruin: for had the work been more advanced than is now the case the Pope would have settled my business(*) for me, and\u00A0I should be rid of all these troubles; but there appears to be much more work involved in destroying a thing than in making it. Yesterday I ran up against a man who told me I was to be made to pay, and that if I had not done so by the end of this month I was going to be punished. I did not believe there was\u00A0any other punishment beside that of Hell fire, or a couple of ducats by way of a fine, even if I were to\u00A0set up a silk merchant\u0027s or a gold-beater\u0027s shop, and were to hire out my earnings as a money-lender. For three hundred years we have paid the taxes\u00A0in Florence, and at one time, at least, I had the\u00A0Proconsolo(**) for my friend. However, I shall have to pay. Everything I have will be seized, for I have not the means to pay at present. I shall come to Rome. If the matter had been settled by agreement I would have sold some of my property and invested in the Monte in such a way that I could have paid my debts\u00A0and still have remained in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"a7805512-e675-4d5a-ae56-af37b377ca61","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":27,"end":27,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"01f91777-09c1-4af1-b5ab-5afd17d8d2ff","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":65,"end":65,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"96275615-5cb7-466d-a7b8-1c7617fa53cd","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":130,"end":130,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"bcdd1433-f5cd-42b5-806d-960e165ca90e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":147,"end":149,"value":"a4393234-2745-42ec-ba3e-42e4c52edb0c","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"938f610f-ab94-485f-b7ff-a760d0c02438","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":181,"end":183,"value":"a4393234-2745-42ec-ba3e-42e4c52edb0c","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"93632cd2-e507-41f7-9222-a766565b3bb7","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":191,"end":191,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3baaa4d5-fff7-41eb-8534-f88dd8b6acf9","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":244,"end":245,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"afbd776f-dbc3-43b0-a7d5-c9c7e872d5f1","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":314,"end":317,"value":"f3a7d77c-f606-47a1-9e65-8a3f8f7c26e0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":["0|0|0|name|Pope Adrian VI","1|1|name|Pope Adrian VI","2|name|Pope Adrian VI"]},{"id":"63fc4cad-fca2-4b4e-af0c-b55491aeb652","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":338,"end":339,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"54cf9e85-013f-41a4-b65f-27edfd9e98d0","type":"codex/entit